<t>CREATE TABLE students ( student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name STRING NOT NULL, student_age INT, student_grade STRING );

CREATE TABLE courses ( course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name STRING NOT NULL, course_description STRING, course_enrollment_limit INT );

CREATE TABLE enrollments ( enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, enrollment_date TIMESTAMP, FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students(student_id), FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id) );

CREATE TABLE assignments ( assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_id INT, assignment_name STRING NOT NULL, assignment_deadline DATE, assignment_max_score INT, FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id) );</t><s>INSERT INTO students (student_id, student_name, student_age, student_grade) SELECT 1, 'Alice', 18, 'A' FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE assignments ( assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_id INT, assignment_name STRING NOT NULL, assignment_deadline DATE, assignment_max_score INT, FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id) );</t><s>insert into courses (course_id, course_name, course_description, course_enrollment_limit) select 1, 'math', 'basic math course', 50 from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE students ( student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name STRING NOT NULL, student_age INT, student_grade STRING );

CREATE TABLE assignments ( assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_id INT, assignment_name STRING NOT NULL, assignment_deadline DATE, assignment_max_score INT, FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id) );</t><s>INSERT INTO assignments (assignment_id, course_id, assignment_name, assignment_deadline, assignment_max_score) SELECT 1, 1, 'Homework 1', '2022-02-01', 100 FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE enrollments ( enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, enrollment_date TIMESTAMP, FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students(student_id), FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id) );

CREATE TABLE courses ( course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name STRING NOT NULL, course_description STRING, course_enrollment_limit INT );</t><s>insert into assignments (assignment_id, course_id, assignment_name, assignment_deadline, assignment_max_score) select 2, 1, 'quiz 1', '2022-02-10', 50 from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE assignments ( assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_id INT, assignment_name STRING NOT NULL, assignment_deadline DATE, assignment_max_score INT, FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id) );</t><s>INSERT INTO assignments (assignment_id, course_id, assignment_name, assignment_deadline, assignment_max_score) SELECT 3, 2, 'Essay 1', '2022-02-05', 80 FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT)

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT) </t><s>insert into teachers (teacher_id, teacher_name, subject, school_id) select 2, 'ms. johnson', 'english', 1 from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) </t><s>INSERT INTO teachers (teacher_id, teacher_name, subject, school_id) SELECT 4, 'Mrs. Wilson', 'History', 2 FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) </t><s>insert into teachers (teacher_id, teacher_name, subject, school_id) select 4, 'mrs. wilson', 'history', 2 from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255))

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) </t><s>insert into courses (course_id, course_name, credit_hours, teacher_id) select 2, 'english composition', 4, 2 from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255))

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)</t><s>INSERT INTO schools (school_id, school_name, location) SELECT 1, 'Lincoln High School', 'New York' FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)</t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 1, 1, 1, to_date('2022-09-01','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) </t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 1, 1, 1, to_date('2022-09-01','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) </t><s>INSERT INTO attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) SELECT 1, 1, 1, TO_DATE('2022-09-01','YYYY-MM-DD') FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) </t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 2, 2, 2, to_date('2022-09-01','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) </t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 2, 2, 2, to_date('2022-09-01','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)</t><s>INSERT INTO attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) SELECT 2, 2, 2, TO_DATE('2022-09-01','YYYY-MM-DD') FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)</t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 3, 3, 3, to_date('2022-09-02','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)</t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 3, 3, 3, to_date('2022-09-02','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) </t><s>INSERT INTO attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) SELECT 3, 3, 3, TO_DATE('2022-09-02','YYYY-MM-DD') FROM dual</s>

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255))

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE attendance (attendance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, date DATE)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) </t><s>insert into attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) select 4, 4, 4, to_date('2022-09-02','yyyy-mm-dd') from dual</s>

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name VARCHAR(255), credit_hours INT, teacher_id INT) 

CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name VARCHAR(255), age INT, school_id INT)

CREATE TABLE schools (school_id INT PRIMARY KEY, school_name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255)) 

CREATE TABLE teachers (teacher_id INT PRIMARY KEY, teacher_name VARCHAR(255), subject VARCHAR(255), school_id INT) </t><s>INSERT INTO attendance (attendance_id, student_id, course_id, date) SELECT 4, 4, 4, TO_DATE('2022-09-02','YYYY-MM-DD') FROM dual</s>
